OL,3,CProbe launched into suspected arson
OL,4,Cattack at Golders Green memorial wall
OL,6,FA memorial wall in Golders Green,
OL,7,Fnorth London, has been targeted in a
OL,8,Fsuspected arson attack.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police said it
OL,11,Freceived reports of a fire at the site
OL,12,Fin Limes Avenue on Monday but the wall
OL,13,Fitself was not damaged.
OL,15,FThe probe is being led by Counter
OL,16,FTerrorism Policing London, supported
OL,17,Fby officers from the North West
OL,18,FCommand Area.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
