OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777464667
OL,3,CProbe launched into suspected arson
OL,4,Cattack at Golders Green memorial wall
OL,6,FPolice have told have told ITV News
OL,7,FLondon "it is not being treated as
OL,8,Fanti-semitic as it is not a Jewish
OL,9,Fmemorial".
OL,11,FThey are also not treating it as a
OL,12,Fterrorist incident and officers are
OL,13,Fkeeping an open mind about the motive
OL,14,Fbehind the attack.
OL,16,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
