OL,3,CProbe launched into suspected arson
OL,4,Cattack at Golders Green memorial wall
OL,6,FIt follows another alleged arson
OL,7,Fattack that saw four Jewish community
OL,8,Fambulances destroyed in Golders Green
OL,9,Fin late March, one of a series of
OL,10,Fapparent attacks targeting Jewish
OL,11,Fsites.
OL,13,FThe memorial wall is a tribute to
OL,14,Fthousands of protesters killed in a
OL,15,Fcrackdown in Iran in January and is
OL,16,Fnear a Jewish centre.
OL,18,FPolice said the suspected arson attack
OL,19,Ftook place at around 12.15am on
OL,20,FMonday, and was reported later that
OL,21,Fday just before 7.30pm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
