FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777464667
OL,3,CProbe launched into suspected arson
OL,4,Cattack at Golders Green memorial wall
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,7,FWilliams, who leads policing in north
OL,8,Fwest London, said: "We recognise that
OL,9,Fthis incident will heighten concerns
OL,10,Fin the Golders Green area, where
OL,11,Fresidents have already faced a series
OL,12,Fof attacks.
OL,14,F"We are working closely with community
OL,15,Forganisations and leaders, and want to
OL,16,Freassure them that our protective
OL,17,Fsecurity operation continues.
OL,19,F"Our local officers are working
OL,20,Fclosely with Counter Terror Policing
OL,21,Fto support their investigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
