OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777464667
OL,3,CProbe launched into suspected arson
OL,4,Cattack at Golders Green memorial wall
OL,6,F"Since last month's attack in Golders
OL,7,FGreen, we have stepped up our work to
OL,8,Freassure communities. This includes
OL,9,Farmed police patrols as well as
OL,10,Fdeployments of officers from Project
OL,11,FServator, who are specially trained to
OL,12,Fspot anyone who may be planning or
OL,13,Fpreparing to commit criminal acts.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
